#

Honey Garlic Sauce

10 min
$2.5
60 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Sauce

Tags:

SauceQuickEasy

Description

A sweet and savory sauce perfect for glazing meats or drizzling over vegetables.

Ingredients

  • honey: 1/2 cup
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • cornstarch: 1 tablespoon
  • water: 2 tablespoons
